ote><br />\n咁請問大堂整個電子時間表<br />\n同埋你去到中環開app有乜分別<br />\n冇人叫你係柴灣開定app睇時間架嘛"},{"pid":"d62334492206cc4cca71650efc270d833019507a","tid":423730,"uid":45374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有app 睇咖喎...</blockquote><br />\n開得app黎架車走左啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打心水清</blockquote><br />\n個app要去到中環先開得架?</blockquote><br />\n你係銅鑼灣開定又有咩用呀<br />\n架車行幾快你又唔知，每個站上落時間你又估唔到，中環站幾多人行你又唔知</blockquote><br />\n咁請問大堂整個電子時間表<br />\n同埋你去到中環開app有乜分別<br />\n冇人叫你係柴灣開定app睇時間架嘛</blockquote><br />\n係條長到嘔既通道易望啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬一電話收唔到都可以用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好過睇啲死人廣告"},{"pid":"36cf92855aa9e92580f0d573c164e5bcf8f630ea","tid":423730,"uid":45374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有app 睇咖喎...</blockquote><br />\nBtw 咩app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMTR Next Train <br />\n<img src=\"http://is4.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple111/v4/b2/57/e9/b257e93b-1377-75ec-acec-ec3115cfe19d/source/392x696bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fis4.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FPurple111%2Fv4%2Fb2%2F57%2Fe9%2Fb257e93b-1377-75ec-acec-ec3115cfe19d%2Fsource%2F392x696bb.jpg&h=95500935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過準唔準就另一回事喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，試試準成度先"}]}